b2f0c0b3cfc22a6292765910ea752e3c2198caba","tid":1412682,"uid":272028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"高質post<br />\n推"},{"pid":"7633c9b88f092befbfff79b1081da2af87f1b80a","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95389ac69b452ead65f9c229bb51b177815df5d1","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a8c0654ea371520313f51ca82830de1e1a2c28","tid":1412682,"uid":260325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9e0a2e88e01f370b1fec9d8c0d8944debea87c4","tid":1412682,"uid":164127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a57763bce83f923162f5529399860d48b27b9ac","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"<em>下文嘅fake news定義為以政治宣傳為目的，故意捏造同散播嘅不實、偏頗資訊。</em><br />\n<br />\n如果係人群中出現一粒tear gas，我地會整熄佢。<br />\n咁係人群中出現一則fake news，點做？<br />\n可能你會話，唔驚啦，我地有fact check呀嘛。<br />\n但Fake news呢家野，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算讀者知道佢係假嘅都依然有效</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\nFake news如果可以達到令讀者相信，當然最好。如果冇辦法取信讀者，仍然有作用。<br />\n人嘅注意力係有限。依家true news (?) 都多到爆炸，再spam 大量fake news ，不斷轟炸讀者，造成疲勞。<br />\n咁多資訊，當中有真有假╴一開始d人仲可以一單單分真假fact check，但係好快耐心精力就會耗盡，於是變得︰<br />\n1)　<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">麻木</span>，進而厭倦，開始唔理之後發生咩事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者，<br />\n2)　<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">混亂</span>，唔知邊啲真邊啲假，進而錯信假新聞，或者拒絕真新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>處理fake news重點就係唔好畀佢侵食更多人嘅注意力</strong></span></span>！<br />\n所以，fact check係多數情況下並唔係針對fake news嘅最佳手段，因為fact check同時都會引起大家對被check嗰件news嘅注意。<br />\n而當注意一個fake news，即係注意一個propaganda，就出事了。<br />\n因為人記住一個論點時，通常<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">只會記得個論點，而唔記得出處</span>！<br />\nthat's why政府每日記者會非常危險。佢日日講抗爭者係暴徒，久而久之就會植入係個腦到。<br />\n我地日日上連登嗌一百次光復香港，就話有免疫力。但係非連登仔呢？一般大眾呢？<br />\n<br />\nfake news係唔同地方（人多vs人少）有唔同處理手法，下面講下如果你係人群之中（如連登、fb page等等多人地方）見到fake news應該點做。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好推，由佢沉</strong></span></span>！<br />\n佢想要你attention，你就唔好畀attention，亦都唔好畀機會佢r到其他人注意。<br />\n如果係連登，可善用新推出嘅「<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">不推post留言功能</span>」（手機beta版限定）<br />\n參考侵侵做法，係下面留低一句「fake news」就上一頁離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgUwNwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgUwNwz.jpg&h=b9c48f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果係fb page等其他地方見到，report post條友，最好report埋個來源，源頭減廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冷處理fake news係最好嘅方法，但如果你真係好想反擊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住唔好逐個反駁，而要陳述事實</span></strong></span>！<br />\n好似前面所講，如果你<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">反駁，其實同時都令fake news嘅agenda得到曝光同討論度</span><br />\n<br />\n假設今日你打開連登，吹水台最頂有以下post︰<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「今日呢單xxxx係假新聞！」\n「突發！xxxx！」\n「已fc！xxxx係假！」\n「唔好信xxxx！」\n「xxxx唔係真，yyyy先係真」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n上面個例子，假新聞xxxx出現得多，定係真野yyyy出現得多？雖然5個post入面有4個係fc post，但係5個post都幫手spam緊「xxxx」呢個term。<br />\n<br />\n如果變成咁呢（zzzz係另一件唔關事嘅真野）︰<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">「yyyy先係真相！」\n「突發！xxxx！」\n「好感動！原來zzzz！」 \n「yyyy！已fact check！」\n「見到zzzz！」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係fb等等地方都可以照做，一旦有人貼假新聞，就拉大隊去spam真野，假一賠十<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係嗰句，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">注意力十分寶貴</span>。<br />\n一眼望落去假新聞版面得少少，唔知點搶fo，收晒皮。<br />\n反觀真野周圍都係，好難唔注意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知係維穩費過咗數定點，政府依家上返晒水。<br />\n假新聞只會越來越多，唔會變少。<br />\n但就好似tear gas一樣，一開始會驚，射多幾次之後就識9秒9淋熄。<br />\nfake news都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港　時代革命</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"好人有好報"},{"pid":"ca97154eb4e303276a66e327457fae4f047a2304","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766fa6a5d17b049cad055b9430cfa8ec12c498a7","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1658e95c3dfcabdbdfd61af56f94dc33a6d6b6","tid":1412682,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69396a8c8067cc0746312d7856921d4429576d67","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b0f9a08508ca9f102457694a7e4acc77e07c726","tid":1412682,"uid":103964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1942173f55bf40745052fc8e8386d23b83dffce1","tid":1412682,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"冷處理好重要<br />\n但問題係連登多左好多五毛<br />\n數量一定破千"},{"pid":"c788f713264e7449fa6e0f4a290d497d5bf9bc64","tid":1412682,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1942173f55bf40745052fc8e8386d23b83dffce1","tid":1412682,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"冷處理好重要<br />\n但問題係連登多左好多五毛<br />\n數量一定破千"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"冇錯，所以我地每一個唔係bot唔係五毛嘅真正人類都要出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}